Homicides: Homicides Cleared in year of occurrence
Annual number of homicides per year: Annual number of homicides that occurred and were cleared in the same year

Homicides: Homicides Cleared that occurred in previous years
Annual number of homicides per year: Annual number of homicides cleared that occurred in previous years

Calculated using the total number of new homicides in a calendar year, and the total number of homicides that are cleared that calendar year – regardless of the year the homicide occurred within.  Total number cleared divided by total number occurred.
